precis:
Amendment to the SEAWAY REGULATIONS clarifying and updating the Seaway
Regulations to reflect current practices, to provide operational
flexibility to Seaway users as well as to ensure that The St. Lawrence
Seaway Authority receives from Seaway users more precise information to
be used to assist in vessel transit planning.
